  "title": "Site Manager (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage daily site operations and coordinate multiple trades on site.</li><li>Ensure adherence to schedule, budget, and safety standards.</li><li>Report progress and maintain proper site documentation.</li><li>Conduct site meetings and provide guidance to supervisors and foremen.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Civil/Construction Engineering or equivalent.</li><li>At least 5 years of experience in <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Strong problem-solving and decision-making capabilities on site.</li><li>Ability to lead site teams effectively.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
